=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\"><i><br></i></span></div><div style=\\\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\\\"><font face=\\\"helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px;\\\"><i>*This illustration is offered for the purposes of education and information only and should not be considered tax or legal advice. For information on your specific situation,&nbsp;</i></span></font><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\"><i>please consult your legal or tax advisor.</i>&nbsp;</span></div>\",\"order\":0},{\"question\":\"Who pays for this benefit? \",\"answer\":\"You pay for the cost of this coverage through payroll deduction.\\n\",\"order\":1},{\"question\":\"How much coverage can I purchase? \",\"answer\":\"This depends on your income level and any other disability coverage you may have in force.\\n\",\"order\":2},{\"question\":\"I already own individual insurance, can I still participate? \",\"answer\":\"YES. A comparison of the IDI plan with any existing coverage can be illustrated for you by calling (888) 986-6677 for additional information.\\n\",\"order\":3},{\"question\":\"What happens if I terminate employment? \",\"answer\":\"Your coverage is individually owned which means you take it with you if you leave the company. Your policy premium will not increase for the life of the policy or until age 67.\",\"order\":4},{\"question\":\"If I use tobacco in any form will it affect my premium?\",\"answer\":\"YES. Your personalized information provides premiums for both tobacco and non-tobacco use. Please provide details (type and usage) of your tobacco use during the application process.\",\"order\":5},{\"question\":\"If I don\'t enroll now, can I participate in the future? \",\"answer\":\"If you do not apply for coverage now, you may be required to provide full medical underwriting in the future if you choose to apply later.\",\"order\":6},{\"questi