"><b>No Medical Exams -&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\">This Guaranteed Standard Issue coverage is applied for by answering a few simple questions</span></i></div><div style=\\\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\\\"><i><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\"><b>Discounted Rates -</b>&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\">25% premium reduction</span></i></div><div style=\\\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\\\"><i><font face=\\\"helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px;\\\"><b>Fixed Premiums &amp; Non-cancellable -</b>&nbsp;</span></font><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\">This benefit is non-cancellable, guaranteed renewable coverage to age 67,&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\">which means as long as you continue to pay your premiums, only you can cancel your policy. Your rates are also guaranteed&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\">never to increase until the expiration date.&nbsp;</span></i></div><div style=\\\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\\\"><i><font face=\\\"helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px;\\\"><b>Tax-free Benefits -</b>&nbsp;</span></font><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\">Since you pay the premiums, you are not subject to taxes.*</span></i></div><div style=\\\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 13px; font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;\\\"><i><br></i></span></div><div style=\\\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\\\"><font face=\\\"helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif\\\"><span s