 are an employee of  CompanyName. Guaranteed standard issue* underwriting allows you to apply for the PlanBranding with no medical exam; however, you will be asked a few medical questions and benefits may be subject to a pre-existing condition limitation.  No medical exam is required if you apply now.  Convenient payroll deduction.\",\"order\":1},{\"question\":\"Who pays for this benefit? \",\"answer\":\"You pay for the cost of this coverage through payroll deduction.\\n\",\"order\":2},{\"question\":\"How much coverage can I purchase? \",\"answer\":\"This depends on your income level and any other disability coverage you may have in force.\\n\",\"order\":3},{\"question\":\"I already own individual insurance, can I still participate? \",\"answer\":\"YES. A comparison of the PlanBranding with any existing coverage can be illustrated for you by calling EnrollNumber  for additional information.\\n\",\"order\":4},{\"question\":\"What happens if I terminate employment? \",\"answer\":\"Your coverage is individually owned which means you take it with you if you leave the company. Your policy premium will not increase until age 65.\",\"order\":5},{\"question\":\"If I use tobacco in any form will it affect my premium?\",\"answer\":\"YES. Your personalized information provides premiums for both tobacco and non-tobacco use. Please provide details (type and usage) of your tobacco use after question 4.\",\"order\":6},{\"question\":\"If I don\'t enroll now, can I participate in the future? \",\"answer\":\"If you do not apply for coverage now, you may be required to provide full medical underwriting in the future if you choose to apply later.\",\"order\":7},{\"question\":\"Can I discontinue coverage at any time? \",\"answer\":\"YES. Premiums will be deducted from your pay each pay period. You may discontinue your participation in this program at any time by calling the Unum CompanyName Policy Services Line at 800-633-7490.\",\"order\":8},{\"question\":\"Can Unum cancel my policy? \