302,30,0,0),(327,175,'logout','You have been successfully logged out.','Logged Out',1436364302,30,0,0),(328,175,'about policy','&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;This benefit offering is comprised of an individual disability insurance (ID) policy offered through sponsorship by your employer. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;You Own The Policy -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This is not a group-owned benefit. Your disability insurance policy belongs to you. You can take the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;policy with you at the same discounted rate if you were to change employers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;No Medical Exams -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This Guaranteed Standard Issue coverage is applied for by answering as few as three simple questions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Discounted Rates -&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;5% premium discount&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Fixed Premiums &amp;amp; Non-cancellable -&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This benefit is non-cancellable, guaranteed renewable coverage to age 65,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;which means as long as you continue to pay your premiums, only you can cancel your policy. Your rates are also guaranteed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;never to increase until the expiration date.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tax-free Benefits -&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Since you pay the premiums, your benefit is not subject to taxes.*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;*This\n publication is offered for the purposes of education and information \nonly and should not be considered tax or legal advice. For information \non your specific situation,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;please consult your legal or tax advisor.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- autocreated page --&gt;','About This Policy',1436364302,30,0,0),(329,175,'about provider','&lt;div class=&quot;span5&quot;&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;box-grey&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0px; width: 100%;&quot;&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Unum is a Fortune 300 insurance company founded in 1848, with corporate headquarters in Chattanooga, Tennessee. &amp;nbsp;Unum is the top disability insurer in both the United States and United Kingdom and also offers other insurance products including accident, critical illness and life insurance. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Unum at a glance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n    &lt;li&gt;Ranks 272 on the Fortune 500 &lt;/li&gt;\n    &lt;li&gt;Protects 20 million people worldwide &lt;/li&gt;\n    &lt;li&gt;Serves the needs of 175,000 businesses in the U.S. and U.K. &lt;/li&gt;\n    &lt;li&gt;Providing benefits for a third of Fortune 500 companies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;span6&quot;&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;In the U.S., Unum is ranked:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul class=&quot;normalUL&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;li&gt;1st in group and individual disability&lt;/li&gt;\n    &lt;li&gt;3rd in voluntary benefits&lt;/li&gt;\n    &lt;li&gt;1st in group life&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- autocreated page --&gt;','About This Provider',1436364302,30,0,0),(331,176,'factsheet','&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;5&quot; color=&quot;#6494b4&quot;&gt;Here are the Facts:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;Worldwide, over one billion people live with some form of disability.&amp;nbsp; Rates of disability are increasing.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;World Health Organization, http://www.who.int/features/factfiles/disability/facts/en/ 2014&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;More than 38 million Americans suffer disabling injuries each year.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;National Safety Council, Injury Facts, 2011 edition.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;Approximately 1 in 3 people will experience some kind of adult onset disability between the ages of 35 and 65.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;Society for Human Resource Management, Job Accommodation Network Conference, &quot;Plan B&quot; by Steven Nissen, August 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;Almost 3 in 10 workers entering the work force today will become disabled before retirement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;Social Security Administration, Fact Sheet, January 31, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;Nearly one in five Americans will become disabled for a year or more before the age of 65.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;Life and Health Insurance Foundation for Education (LIFE), &quot;Disability Insurance: Who Needs It?&quot; May 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;A Medical crisis contributes to half of all mortgage foreclosures.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;Get Sick, Get Out: The Medical Causes of Home Mortgage Foreclosures, Robertson, Egelhof &amp;amp; Hoke&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;Disability causes nearly 50% of all mortgage foreclosures, compared to 2% that are caused by loss of life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;WPLG, Miami, &quot;Disability Insurance Offers Vital Protection,&quot; July 31, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;Approximately one in three people will experience some kind of adult-onset disability between the ages of 35 and 65, such as arthritis, lupus, diabetes, spinal cord injuries, mental disorders, or MS.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;SHRM, Job Accommodation Network Conference &quot;&#39;Plan B&#39; Needed for Adult-Onset Disabilities Such as MS,&quot; speech by Steven Nissen, director of employment programs for the National Multiple Sclerosis Society, August 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;Since 2000, the number of disabled workers in America has increased by 35% while the financial health of many American workers has declined.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;Council for Disability Awareness, &quot;Misinformation, Poor Planning Can Threaten Financial Security,&quot; March 7, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;56 % of U.S. adults surveyed say they would not be able to pay their bills or meet expenses if they became disabled and could not work for a year or longer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;National Association of Insurance Commissioners, &quot;Majority of Americans Unprepared for Financial Impact of Disability,&quot; February 28, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;A survey of American workers shows that nine out of 10 workers underestimate their chance of becoming disabled.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Council for Disability Awareness, &quot;Most Workers Underestimate Chances, Impact of Disability, Survey Shows,&quot; March 7, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;Most disabling injuries suffered by American workers occur off the job and are not covered by workers&#39; compensation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;National Safety Council, Injury Facts, 2005-2006 edition.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;The average monthly Social Security Disability Insurance benefit is only $978.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;Social Security Administration, Fact Sheet, January 31, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;About two-thirds of initial applications are denied and the wait for appeals can take as long as three years.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;The New York Times, &quot;Disability Cases Last Longer as Backlog Rises,&quot; by Erik Eckholm, December 10, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- autocreated page --&gt;','Fact Sheet',1438691495,30,0,0),(332,176,'decline','Do you wish to decline this coverage?&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;Please use the area below to let us know why you are declining.&lt;/div&gt;','Decline',1438691495,30,0,0),(333,176,'contact','&lt;br&gt;','Contact Us',1438691495,30,0,0),(334,176,'apply now','When you click the apply now button you will be transferred to the insurance carrier&#39;s website to complete the simplified enrollment process.&lt;!-- autocreated page --&gt;','Apply Now',1438691495,30,0,0),(335,176,'return from carrier','&lt;!-- autocreated page 