ts, 2005-2006 edition.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n\n&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;The average monthly Social Security Disability Insurance benefit is only $978.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n\n&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;Social Security Administration, Fact Sheet, January 31, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p class=&quot;h4&quot;&gt;About two-thirds of initial applications are denied and the wait for appeals can take as long as three years.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n\n&lt;p class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;The New York Times, &quot;Disability Cases Last Longer as Backlog Rises,&quot; by Erik Eckholm, December 10, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;!-- autocreated page --&gt;','Fact Sheet',1439471664,30,0,0),(350,178,'error','&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;There was an error submitting your application.&amp;nbsp; Please contact us at\n&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;5&quot; color=&quot;#6494b4&quot;&gt;(888) 640-8470&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;br&gt;','Error Submitting Application',1439471713,30,0,0),(351,178,'logout','You have been successfully logged out.','Logged Out',1439471713,30,0,0),(352,178,'about policy','&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Individual Disability Insurance (IDI) programs offer individually owned insurance policies offered in a multi-life setting. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;IDI coverage is offered through a simplified underwriting process (Guaranteed Standard Issue)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Level premium structure to your age 65&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;