ut.','Logged Out',1462294644,30,0,0),(498,192,'about policy','&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Individual Disability Insurance (IDI) programs offer individually owned insurance policies offered in a multi-life setting. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;IDI coverage is offered through a simplified underwriting process (Guaranteed Standard Issue)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Level premium structure to your age 65&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Policy type is a non-cancelable and guaranteed renewable contract&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Coverage is portable (take it with you if you leave the company)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Discounted 30% from ‘retail’ rates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Able to cover total compensation over and above the existing Group LTD plan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Since you pay the premiums, benefits would not generally be considered non-taxable.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- autocreated page --&gt;','About This Policy',1462294644,30,0,0),(499,192,'about provider','&lt;div&gt;At Unum, we’re in the business of helping people through difficult \ntimes in their lives. Our financial protection benefits provide \nindividuals and their families with the financial security they need to \nbetter cope with the loss of a loved one or the inability to work due to\n illness or injury.&lt;/div